{"tid":545967,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【持續寒冷】料明早市區低見7°C 達嚴寒水平勢破入冬紀錄","createTime":"2018-01-31T04:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T06:41:12.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b34b007992d8ec65c79912e28775f9fa3e9a63fc","tid":545967,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n凍死人啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180131/57775163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57775163&d=LRUMzfhORgM2aOm%2BMWXlhcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=3cf05615\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57775163&h=6e5412ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180131/57775163</a><br />\n<br />\n天文台於今早更新九天天氣預報，預測明天早上將會天氣嚴寒，市區氣溫低見7&deg;C，料會低過本月9日錄得的7.9&deg;C，創今年最低氣溫紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指出，冬季季候風及其補充會維持華南的寒冷天氣至下周後期。受一股乾燥大陸氣流影響，該區漸轉天晴乾燥，日夜溫差較大。明天起，本港天氣將逐漸好轉，見番陽光，惟因冷空氣補充及有所加強，預料明天及下周一，市區氣溫均有機會低見7&deg;C，達嚴寒水平，由「濕凍」變為「乾凍」。大家要注意保暖，及關心身邊的老友記。"},{"pid":"cd61d37167bfce9f67c5a43339f39eca518d4b8d","tid":545967,"uid":77571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"香港濕凍"}]}